At RoxyChima, 
We Offer the following programmes in partnership with Think Big Institute, Umuahia:

    Advanced ICT (Web development and programming)
    Solar panel assembly and installations
    Fiberglass productions
    Plastic recycling and production
    Media Production and publications
    Agriculture and allied products
    Automobile mechanism, maintenance and security.
    Building technology
    Catering
    Event management and public 
    
We are a passionate entrepreneural startup firm with interest in civil, electrical projects and providing entrepreneural development training to the teeming youths of the South-Eastern part of Nigeria. 
